                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "When drow capture a particularly hated surface elf, or one with a large following, they inflict even greater pain upon them during the fleshwarping process than most other victims. The resulting irnakurse are known as \u201cmockeries,\u201d and always have <a aonid=\"790\" game-obj=\"Rules\">elite adjustments</a>. Rather than using them, drow keep them close at hand as living \u201cart\u201d akin to a pet or trophy."
            },
